	<h1 class="title">索尼、亚马逊也要做AR眼镜，这玩意怎么就成了大公司标配</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73517/small/73517.jpg?1431406847" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">赖江锟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-19 15:15:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16265/medium/16265.jpg?1445235768" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


